---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Cookie Policy">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Cookie Policy</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: November 1, 2025</p>

      <h2>What Are Cookies?</h2>
      <p>
        Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit websites. They help websites remember your preferences and understand how you use the site.
      </p>

      <h2>Cookies We Use</h2>

      <h3>Google Analytics Cookies</h3>
      <p>
        We use Google Analytics to understand how visitors use Nonprofit.ai. These cookies collect information such as:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Which pages you visit</li>
        <li>How long you stay on each page</li>
        <li>What device and browser you're using</li>
        <li>General location (city/country)</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        <strong>Cookie names:</strong> _ga, _gid, _gat
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Purpose:</strong> Analytics and site improvement
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Duration:</strong> Up to 2 years
      </p>

      <h3>Cookie Consent Cookie</h3>
      <p>
        We set a cookie to remember your cookie consent choice.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Purpose:</strong> Remember your consent preferences
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Duration:</strong> 1 year
      </p>

      <h2>Managing Cookies</h2>

      <h3>Through Our Site</h3>
      <p>
        You can manage your cookie preferences using the consent banner that appears on your first visit, or by clicking "Manage Cookies" in the footer.
      </p>

      <h3>Through Your Browser</h3>
      <p>
        You can also control cookies through your browser settings:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://support.google.com/chrome/answer/95647" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Chrome</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/enhanced-tracking-protection-firefox-desktop" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Firefox</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://support.apple.com/guide/safari/manage-cookies-sfri11471/mac" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Safari</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-edge/delete-cookies-in-microsoft-edge-63947406-40ac-c3b8-57b9-2a946a29ae09" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Edge</a></li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Opt Out of Google Analytics</h3>
      <p>
        You can opt out of Google Analytics across all websites by installing the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>Impact of Declining Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        If you decline cookies:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>The site will still work perfectly</li>
        <li>We won't collect analytics data about your visit</li>
        <li>All prompts and features remain accessible</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Updates to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this Cookie Policy. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about cookies? Contact us at <a href="mailto:leigh@ppm.io">leigh@ppm.io</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
